14 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
15 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
16 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 6-187E of Title 70, unless there
17 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
18 A. The Commission for Educational Quality and Accountability
19 shall establish student teaching requirements for teacher candidates
20 who are enrolled in an educator preparation program accredited by
21 the Commission. The requirements shall include:
22 1. Completion of a minimum number of weeks of field experience;
