1 2. Completion of a qualified job-embedded, competency-based
2 teacher registered apprenticeship program. For the purposes of this
3 section, “teacher registered apprenticeship program” means a
4 structured program that combines on-the-job training with academic
5 instruction to prepare individuals to become teachers.
6 B. The Commission shall promulgate rules to implement the
7 provisions of this act.
8 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective July 1, 2025.
9 SECTION 3. It being immediately necessary for the preservation
10 of the public peace, health, or safety, an emergency is hereby
11 declared to exist, by reason whereof this act shall take effect and
12 be in full force from and after its passage and approval.
